elements.expression:
shape "square" fill="#444444" border="rgba(255,255,255,0)" borderWidth=0 maintainAspect=false
| render

shape "square" fill="#20394F" border="rgba(255,255,255,0)" borderWidth=0 maintainAspect=false
| render

| render

shape "square" fill="#0038B1" border="rgba(255,255,255,0)" borderWidth=0 maintainAspect=false
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT AVG(oil_usage) usage
FROM dc_energy
WHERE oil_usage IS NOT NULL"
| math "usage"
| formatNumber "0.0a"
| metric "KGAL" 
  metricFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=48 align="left" color="#FFFFFF" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false} 
  labelFont={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=24 align="left" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false}
| render

filters
| essql query="SELECT SUM(ghg_emissions) ghg FROM dc_energy"
| markdown "Total GHG Emissions: " {getCell "ghg" | formatNumber "0.0a"} " metric tons CO2e" 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=24 align="center" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false}
| render

filters
| essql 
  query="SELECT COUNT(*) total, report_status
FROM dc_energy
GROUP BY report_status"
| pointseries x="total" y="report_status" color="report_status"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle bars=0.75 horizontalBars=true color="#444444"} legend=false xaxis=false
| render

filters
| demodata
| markdown "CHOOSE YEAR BUILT"
| render

essql query="SELECT year_built
FROM dc_energy"
| dropdownControl valueColumn="year_built" filterColumn="year_built"
| render
